sentences: Ilona Breģe (born 20 May 1959 in Riga, Soviet Union) is a composer, pianist and musicologist.
She graduated the Latvian Music Academy (former State Conservatory) as pianist (1983) and composer (1986), Doctor of Art (1993).

Breģe was solo pianist in the Latvian Philharmonic (1983–92), researcher in the Latvian Science Academy in the Literature, Folklore and Art department (1992–98), General Manager of the Latvian National Symphony Orchestra (1997–2006).
